nodes.text: The MC75 Armored Cruiser was a variant of the MC75 Star Cruiser produced by Mon Calamari Shipyards. After the subjugation of Mon Cala, these vessels were the first wave of city-ships as part of the Mon Calamari Exodus Fleet, led by the Profundity, and integrated into the Alliance Fleet of the Rebel Alliance.
